Description:
High, beautiful, elegant and distinguished *The Canadian Tower,* an urban architecture that takes part of the history of Montreal. In addition to its prime location, in the heart of the City, where urban and city life vibrates ... This Condo is part of it, so be part of the history!
To live in this Condo is an intelligent choice. It offers you all the best: Brightness, modernity, contemporary layout and design, high end appliances and stunning views.
The building also offers you a multitude of services both internally and externally.

Condo Features:
- Nice bedroom + office than can be used as 2nd bedroom
- Open space arrangement
- Modern kitchen with high-end appliances;
- Premium laminate flooring;
- Integrated island in the kitchen;
- Recessed lighting in the kitchen;
- Windows from floor to ceiling;
- 50th floor with nice and open view
- A garage is included

Services of the building:
- Luxury reception
- Concierge service and security 24/7
- Training room inspired by the Montreal Canadiens;
- Spa with hydrotherapy in rainwater and sauna;
- Outdoor and heated in-ground pool
- Outdoor panoramic terrace on the roof with barbecue, fireplaces
- 3 reception rooms equipped with giant screen televisions
- Games room with pool table and Montreal Canadiens souvenirs collection;
- Sports bar and restaurant;
- Bicycle storage;

Approximate:
- Direct access to the Lucien-L'Allier metro station, suburban trains, Via Rail stations and Windsor Station;
- Close to major motorways 
- Direct access to the Bell Center and Montreal Canadiens store
- Within walking distance of the financial district, Crescent Street, Concordia University, McGill University and many shops, restaurants, bars, hospitals, etc.
- Located in front of a future Provigo / Loblaw grocery store, a SAQ branch and a smart grill restaurant....

